    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>Veloras was said to have been born (extracted from the Life Stream) when the <strong>Primordial Arcanum</strong> realized that they needed a keeper of truths. </p><p>It is Veloras who records everything in the Codex Eternal. </p><p>It was by his power that memories of the gods were erased from Elarans during <strong>The Sundering</strong></p><p>It is also said that Veloras knows every lie ever spoken and keeps them preserved in glass jars, whispering them back to their liars on deathbeds.</p>"
